  "texts": [
    "As for the present proposed regulatory model, there are several stakeholders that need to be considered: the state organizations, international organizations, business players, the regulatory body itself, the democratic base (i.e.",
    "courts and politicians), potentially the auditors, and the users.",
    "All of these actors have what might be referred to as a partial responsibility, each for the things they are tasked to do.",
    "First, the state organizations are required to oversee the developments with due care and to report adequately.",
    "Second, the international organizations have to be held accountable for the correct guidance according to the latest knowledge in what AI can do and where the risks lie."
  ],
